SpeedRacer
To play, follow the steps below:
1. Install JRE (Java Runtime Environment): 
		sudo apt-get install openjdk-7-jre (on Debian based linux distros)
	or Download it here: http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
2. Download the game:
	zip:
	tar.xz:
3. Extract the file
	zip: unzip filename
	tar.xz: tar xJvf filename
4. If you have joysticks, run it with: 
		java -jar -Djava.library.path=jinput SpeedRacer.jar 
	If you don't have, simply run: 
		java -jar SpeedRacer.jar
5. Enjoy the game